    <node id="World Athletics Federation">
      <data key="d0">World Athletics Federation</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">The World Athletics Federation is the governing body overseeing the World Athletics Championship and record validations. Established to regulate and promote the sport of athletics globally, the federation ensures the standardization and recognition of athletic records. It plays a crucial role in organizing major international competitions, including the World Athletics Championships, which bring together top athletes from around the world. The federation's responsibilities extend to validating and maintaining official records, ensuring fairness and consistency in the sport. Through its efforts, the World Athletics Federation aims to foster the growth and development of athletics, supporting both elite athletes and grassroots participation.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation is the governing body overseeing the World Athletics Championship and record validations.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation is the governing body overseeing the World Athletics Championship and record validations.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-4b4b32da40de7c315d4fc5bc3606929d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1bb5cd9ff264b572149867bd71c495b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f7439dbf996487e31403af55f8698e05&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a404f2d31665f96ab0e88a96f2a90ee3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1bfb07eaab27897458cab13d267cc8d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1685d87806fa322636a0ae38b55d67c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc07254d5813505d444e17ebbf3f2b20&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec40f4f99f237f110c130f565fcdafb2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-10e08cee194615ba03bf33209aec912f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-97c80096294904a558b964416e5ccaf8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f95474afc1013b7a1202708d01d2dc0f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0dbc491114ff8705fba2c9e7e3ed9a4a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-560b8be5e9e6bb31c2d16928238b2b7a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6131f0df12a523211a65cb7ece1c07c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c8e2fa5b3eace62b3886022e12939ae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d2b3198b39b98b16e57ae034086b62f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e57bc6873c66490eea565796c278c65c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5e8823423a618b170916e397799b508&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4481863e0d9908d077eeecd8356a8ce2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a4c2c97ee31ddb939c8237c792d072f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c31f0114f2d60c12fd8bdf0ee661a83c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b39a6a6a4109abd7548ecd643633a38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-400872ec1480585ca928963cebc19aa1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75de94603a7bff182d11ab7ef1a01606&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e2f0cd323caa27d965dd1caae57b78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-267ad18ddac0cc597ffc75b79a8c8644&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2b485abcfc308d2d94ae05bd53adb073&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38aa0db558c709d4aebdee61670b1024&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd231d2bd8414ef8c9e97c92d73da8c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06330342d0ee4db5e1dcfd59f2db5fe1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2515eeb9fcb1e397327067d3a5434bb4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef659a17cc2a3bd6be181bbda500e6a4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-671ebe8c52f8fa8e6f8e00802adc7d3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed8b7f6c5d32971500da73eb5ea12d64&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29978db7bc5e506c68fb30ffdffbef86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-be45792a9b99f98546b237e51ec0bad4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1642c2814e435f78be96f063cd8f1811&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c8007fa57e6d9fe3d3ca4183a69440d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc22a62b44adbcf1244ac1df897d453d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42dd8c32bb8185e33d363bb341ef97e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5968153bab2c