ff0a692ed9e8dcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19f58bce6d34e04dd90b4aff78fa74b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5554e2648391bd99c697fcf0ae8a528&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5dabb1554253b604ceb84e902345e41a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-767835a035f83fca2664d7156bdb857b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ecf9351c2a05d954d78e3a5268a94f84&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da697a87c71cca2f7b275780344af1d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b4742b2619b60c4229952c7ad057ba69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8698f5ffec521d5bdc5d5157982f39d2</data>
      <data key="d2">Noah Carter's record is validated by the World Athletics Federation.</data>
