    <node id="Cannes Film Festival">
      <data key="d0">Cannes Film Festival</data>
      <data key="d1">event</data>
      <data key="d2">The Cannes Film Festival is an annual film festival held in Cannes, France. It is one of the most prestigious events in the film industry, known for showcasing a wide range of cinematic works from around the world. The festival has a long history of recognizing outstanding films and directors, contributing significantly to the global film community.

Notable films and directors have been honored at the Cannes Film Festival. For instance, Paweł Pawlikowski won the Best Director prize for his film *Cold War*. Additionally, *The Marquise of O* won the Grand Prix Spécial Prize in 1976. The festival has also been the premiere venue for significant films such as *The Man Who Knew Too Much* (1956), which premiered on April 29, 1956.

The Cannes Film Festival has featured a variety of films in competition and special screenings. *Les Chansons d'amour* was selected for competition in 2007, and *Les Côtelettes* was entered in 2003. Other notable entries include *Paris Vice Squad*, which was entered in 1951, and *Qivitoq*, which was nominated for the Golden Palm. These examples highlight the festival's role in promoting both established and emerging cinematic talents.&lt;SEP&gt;The Cannes Film Festival is an annual film festival held in Cannes, France, where Remote Control was screened in the Un Certain Regard section.&lt;SEP&gt;The Cannes Film Festival is where Ręce Do Góry was screened out of competition in 1981.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a404f2d31665f96ab0e88a96f2a90ee3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c52331902726c49c09c96e0e1d1bfb4e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2acf50ee69c8d584ada8e02ed28e9261&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c964718d02482f357275fdf774f6b32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0fbfa6e6327c417834acbfbaac15def&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21dabad0d1d7b464aced5aa1f5f98a74&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b416e9c268ef6ec82c9d9d035b00d84&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-558d256d9744abd4ad191491b9519f76&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f0fdb27914b4fb43833841a0d025ec21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b1f0748daa6aa0f14a8e76004cdb149</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
