      <data key="d0">Moscow International Film Festival</data>
      <data key="d1">event</data>
      <data key="d2">The Moscow International Film Festival is an event where Den kære familie was entered.&lt;SEP&gt;The Moscow International Film Festival is an event where "Fire in Hell" made its international premiere in 2012.&lt;SEP&gt;The Moscow International Film Festival is an event where Bertrand Blier's film How Much Do You Love Me? was entered in 2005.&lt;SEP&gt;The Moscow International Film Festival is an event where "The Four Days of Naples" won the FIPRESCI Prize in 1963.</data>
