    <node id="Lollia Paulina">
      <data key="d0">Lollia Paulina</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Lollia Paulina, also known as Lollia Paullina, was a Roman Empress for six months in 38 AD as the third wife of Caligula. She was a noble Roman woman who lived in the Roman Empire of the 1st century.</data>
