    <node id="Roman Empire">
      <data key="d0">Roman Empire</data>
      <data key="d1">location</data>
      <data key="d2">The Roman Empire was the political entity ruled by emperors such as Caligula, Tiberius, and others.&lt;SEP&gt;The Roman Empire was a political entity where Theoderic the Great served as a patrician.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-8d2b3198b39b98b16e57ae034086b62f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-10d01be05e412f607f7a3beabe14dde7</data>
