    <node id="Rome">
      <data key="d0">Rome</data>
      <data key="d1">location</data>
      <data key="d2">Rome is the capital of the Roman Empire, where Caligula initiated construction projects and ruled as emperor.&lt;SEP&gt;Rome is the city where Henry III was crowned Emperor by Pope Clement II.&lt;SEP&gt;Rome is a city where René Poupardin spent a significant part of his life.&lt;SEP&gt;Rome is a city in Italy where Caterina Sforza gained her freedom.&lt;SEP&gt;Rome is the city near where Nanni Loy died in 1995.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-8d2b3198b39b98b16e57ae034086b62f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b4b611eaf424d0081ac1c42593cfd38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7f0c61af6251dc3a86ef278894b5ab16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad0c3097983e0f6f6ae9f6da9f7dee67&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4dc8485a05c7210da055c81aee47af08</data>
