    <node id="Antonio González Flores">
      <data key="d0">Antonio González Flores</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Antonio González Flores was a Spanish singer-songwriter and actor of Romani descent on his father's side. He was the son of Antonio González and Lola Flores, and had two sisters, Lolita Flores and Rosario Flores. He was divorced from Ana Villa and had a daughter named Alba.</data>
