      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Prince Frederick of Hesse-Kassel was a member of the dynasty that ruled the Landgraviate of Hesse-Kassel, a Danish general, and the youngest son of Hereditary Prince Frederick of Hesse-Kassel and Princess Mary of Great Britain. He was born on 11 September 1747 and died on 20 May 1837.</data>
