      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Queen Victoria ascended to the throne one month after Prince Frederick of Hesse-Kassel's death and was the granddaughter of his first cousin King George III.&lt;SEP&gt;Queen Victoria was the monarch of the United Kingdom from 1837 to 1901, and George Thomas Orlando Bridgeman served as her chaplain from 1872.</data>
