    <node id="Henry">
      <data key="d0">Henry</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Henry is a king known for his piety, religious ceremonies, and charitable donations. He extracted money from Jews, introduced the Statute of Jewry, and faced rebellions during his rule.</data>
