    <node id="Adelaide">
      <data key="d0">Adelaide</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Adelaide was the wife of Louis I and the mother of Louis II. Her parentage is unknown, and she died after 1025.&lt;SEP&gt;Adelaide, also known as Athelheidhe, was the wife of Gero II.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-758a0a6b7851ac012d0c9fd434d94410&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e15b5cfb960e6df463bd760535ebe6fa</data>
