      <data key="d0">Roman Rite</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The Roman Rite is a liturgical rite used in the celebration of Mass in the Roman Catholic Church, implemented by Remigius of Rouen in the Gallic church.</data>
