    <node id="Empress Xu">
      <data key="d0">Empress Xu</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Empress Xu, formally known as Empress Renxiaowen, was the empress consort to the Yongle Emperor and the third empress of China's Ming dynasty. She was well educated and compiled bibliographies of virtuous women.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-f58fec195d8efa9069d2477d8a930f4c</data>
