      <data key="d0">Prince Gustav of Thurn and Taxis</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Prince Gustav of Thurn and Taxis, born Gustav Otto Maximilian Lamoral of Thurn and Taxis, was the sixth child of Maximilian Karl, 6th Prince of Thurn and Taxis, and Princess Mathilde Sophie of Oettingen-Oettingen and Oettingen-Spielberg. He was born on 2 February 1848 in Regensburg, Kingdom of Bavaria.</data>
