      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Princess Mathilde Sophie of Oettingen-Oettingen and Oettingen-Spielberg was the second wife of Maximilian Karl, 6th Prince of Thurn and Taxis, and the mother of Prince Gustav of Thurn and Taxis. She was born on 9 February 1816 in Oettingen, Kingdom of Bavaria, and died on 20 January 1886 in Obermais, Meran, County of Tyrol, Austria-Hungary.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c44a0aa42d1d9547ae3cd28845385d01</data>
