      <data key="d1">location</data>
      <data key="d2">Paris is the birthplace and deathplace of Napoléon Alexandre Berthier and the birthplace of Alexandre Berthier.&lt;SEP&gt;Paris is a city where René Poupardin spent most of his life.&lt;SEP&gt;Paris is the city where Christophe Honoré moved to in 1995.&lt;SEP&gt;Paris is the capital of France and the location of the Royal Basilica of Saint Denis.&lt;SEP&gt;Paris is the city where Alex Joffé died.</data>
