      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Prince Bernhard Lucas Emmanuel of Orange-Nassau, van Vollenhoven is the second son of Princess Margriet of the Netherlands and Pieter van Vollenhoven, born on 25 December 1969. He was previously a member of the Dutch Royal House and eleventh in the line of succession to the Dutch throne.</data>
