      <data key="d0">Demetrius III</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Demetrius III was one of Seleucus VI's brothers who became involved in the civil war after Antiochus X killed Antiochus XI.&lt;SEP&gt;Demetrius III succeeded Antiochus X in Antioch and controlled the capital in 88/87 BC.</data>
