      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Cleopatra IV of Egypt was Queen of Egypt briefly from 116 to 115 BC, jointly with her husband Ptolemy IX Lathyros, and later became queen consort of Syria as the wife of Antiochus IX Cyzicenus.</data>
