    <node id="Maurya Emperor Ashoka">
      <data key="d0">Maurya Emperor Ashoka</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Ashoka, also known as Ashoka the Great, was an Indian emperor of the Maurya Dynasty who ruled almost all of the Indian subcontinent from 232 BCE. He promoted the spread of Buddhism across ancient Asia.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c441fc08420b5ae39ad39901be0e214c</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1782057678</data>
