    <node id="Prince Franz De Paula Of Liechtenstein">
      <data key="d0">Prince Franz De Paula Of Liechtenstein</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Prince Franz De Paula Of Liechtenstein, also known as Franz De Paula Joachim Joseph, was born on 25 February 1802 in Vienna and died on 31 March 1887 in Vienna. He was a son of Johann I Joseph, Prince of Liechtenstein, and Landgravine Josepha of Fürstenberg-Weitra, and had notable familial connections within the Liechtenstein royal family.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c181891c0f7c96314618fd1dffd471fc</data>
