      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Prince John Konstantinovich of Russia, also known as Prince Ioann, Prince Ivan, or Prince Johan, was the eldest son of Grand Duke Konstantin Konstantinovich of Russia and Yelizaveta Mavrikievna. He was described as a gentle, religious person and was nicknamed "Ioannchik" by his relatives.</data>
