      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Joan of Châtillon, also known as Jeanne de Blois, was Countess of Blois from 1280 to 1291 and Lady of Avesnes. She was the daughter of John I, Count of Blois, and Alix of Brittany, Dame de Pontarcy.</data>
