    <node id="Anastasia of Serbia">
      <data key="d0">Anastasia of Serbia</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Anastasia of Serbia, also known as Ana, was the princess consort of the Serbian Principality and the wife of Stefan Nemanja. She took monastic vows in 1196 and was baptized as Anastasia.</data>
