    <node id="Eleonora di Garzia di Toledo">
      <data key="d0">Eleonora di Garzia di Toledo</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Eleonora di Garzia di Toledo, also known as Leonora or Dianora, was the daughter of García Álvarez de Toledo, 4th Marquis of Villafranca, Duke of Fernandina. She was born in Florence, raised by Cosimo I de' Medici and Eleanor of Toledo, and married Pietro de' Medici. Her life ended tragically when she was strangled by her husband.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-4f3b15e0b68c65251ff0a692ed9e8dcd</data>
