    <edge source="World Athletics Federation" target="World Athletics Championship">
      <data key="d7">13.0</data>
      <data key="d8">The World Athletics Federation oversees the World Athletics Championship and validates records set during the event. This governing body ensures the integrity and standardization of athletic competitions, including the World Athletics Championship, by establishing and enforcing rules, regulations, and record-keeping protocols. The federation's role is crucial in maintaining the credibility and global recognition of the championship, which serves as a premier platform for athletes to showcase their skills and achieve record-breaking performances. Through its oversight, the World Athletics Federation plays a pivotal part in the development and promotion of athletics worldwide.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees the World Athletics Championship and validates records set during the event.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees the World Athletics Championship and validates records set during the event.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees the World Athletics Championship and validates records set during the event.</data>
      <data key="d9">event organization,record validation</data>
      <data key="d10">chunk-9909443b3a6fe3195194ada7a6c96443&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c18d3be96f5c78095f48818f929e003&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0df7bb43f11ed0032a41039ac3851f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0631fdd5fc22de0f69204b4714585e74&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-038ad8f7ee659ffd1b49b2d756cda356&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3557f799425e012d25a6725d87a8d29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3fb103f6be17aa5a32948254ba9ad52a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a9f536116dfd51af36daf47134c0d59c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19d5ef4141d49c2aa229153f800c6c98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5374c31ba5f8d4ba6ee940ca8638bff0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9cf5be1d5d35308cb8be9c3f55f2503e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d1b6caa4cbb7b44aab00b82ad07f933a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f7c9556af695435a96540a9f84521149</data>
      <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d12">1782060957</data>
      <data key="d13" />
    </edge>
    <edge source="John Beach" target="Sac and Fox Tribes">
      <data key="d7">1.0</data>
      <data key="d8">John Beach served as the last U.S. Indian Agent to the Sac and Fox tribes and negotiated a treaty for the purchase of land in Iowa.</data>
      <data key="d9">Indian Agent,Treaty Negotiation</data>
      <data key="d10">chunk-d1bb5cd9ff264b572149867bd71c495b</data>
      <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
