      <data key="d13" />
    </edge>
    <edge source="Henry" target="Lusignans">
      <data key="d7">1.0</data>
      <data key="d8">The notoriety of Henry's Poitevin half-brothers, the Lusignans, contributed to his unpopularity.</data>
      <data key="d9">family notoriety,political unpopularity</data>
